<p><b>How old is Fitz in the first Keeper of the Lost Cities book?</b> First apperance Fitzroy "Fitz" Avery Vacker is a seventeen-year-old elf, as of Legacy. He is normally called Fitz, a shortened version of Fitzroy, but is also called "Wonderboy" by Dex Dizznee and "Fitzy", "Fitzter", and "Lord of the Snuggles" by Keefe Sencen.</p>
<p><b>Who is Fitz in Keeper of the Lost Cities?</b> Fitzroy Avery Vacker (Fitz) He's a loyal brother, a model prodigy, and tends to earn his nickname,“Wonderboy” (despite the fact that Dex meant the name sarcastically). And even though he's two grade levels ahead of Sophie, Fitz cares about her more than she knows (more than he knows, honestly).</p>
