<p><b>Where is Exile kotlc?</b> Exile is the Elves' most secure prison. It is located within the center of the Earth, and was excavated by the dwarves for elven use. The elves use Exile to store prisoners, political prisoners (barring humans), storing individuals for whom the council has ordered a mind break, and storing those with broken minds.</p>
